waken /ˈweɪkən/

(wakening,wakened,wakens) 

1. V-T/V-I When you waken , or when someone or something wakens you, you wake from sleep. 使醒来; 醒来 [文学性] 

例： The noise outside wakened her. 那外面的噪声吵醒了她。 

